snippet.title: Westmark Manor Final Trailer
snippet.description:
THE FINAL TRAILER AND RELEASE DATE ARE HERE! 



Do you have what it takes?

Westmark Manor is a journey into the occult, a mind-bending survival horror game, with a heavy focus on solving puzzles and exploration, inspired by the formidable H.P. Lovecraft.


This is the very first project to be a part of Toadman's initiative to publish personal projects developed by our own employees and we couldn't be more proud of this one!

So, if you are ready to dive into a dark, mysterious game, and solve the puzzles guarding the secrets locked deep within Westmark Manor, head on over to the Steam store page and wishlist it now, and show the darkness some love!

Developed by Nodbrim Interactive - http://nodbrim.com
Published by Toadman Interactive - https://toadmaninteractive.com
Wishlist on Steam now: https://bit.ly/2xYAje8
Follow us on Twitter: https://bit.ly/3bK3gt2
Facebook page: https://bit.ly/2xdvEVx
Join our Discord: https://bit.ly/3bHE86n
